---
title: Sweet Chili Chicken Lettuce Wrap with Chicken Thighs, Bell Pepper & Candied Peanuts
description: Our chefs came up with the perfect filling for fresh, crisp romaine leaves: Sautéed ground turkey and bell pepper simmered in a chili-soy sauce, candied peanuts for another layer of crunch, and cilantro for even more green freshness. Get ready to be wowed by the wrap.
